{"TopicId":194964,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Who wants kerbal helmets to smash if you hit the ground hard enough?","CreatedByName":"Jurassic kerbal","CreatedById":205632,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-22T19:45:23Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jurassic kerbal","CreatedById":205632,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-22T19:45:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u2019t but I am just curious on this topic and what people think.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commodore_32","CreatedById":200414,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-22T19:47:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWE NEED THIS\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T03:35:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBefore the parachutes the Kerbium helmets were the only way to save a falling Kerbal.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd, well, for me they still are as I keep forgetting about the personal chutes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RoninFrog","CreatedById":203049,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T04:07:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure it would be very comforting to have a whole bunch of dead kerbals lying around the ground with their helmets smashed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-06-23T04:11:18Z\u0022 title=\u002206/23/2020 04:11  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJune 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by RoninFrog\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EWhoopsie, posted in the wrong thread, now I gotta say something relevant!\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yaivenov","CreatedById":81754,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T04:08:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs a difficulty option though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe an intermediate cosmetic-only setting of a cracked and leaking visor too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T13:37:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith constantly popped Kerbal eyes unlikely we could see a difference.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T13:42:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh great another reason to hate when they ragdoll down a slope.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T13:47:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d enjoy it if the helmet cracked, but then I\u0027d also like Kerbals to vomit inside their helmets, so I\u0027m probably a minority.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved this to Suggestions\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T13:56:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy are you guys dropping kerbals on their heads? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T14:03:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223807993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194964\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221592920613\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy are you guys dropping kerbals on their heads? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there some other way?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-23T14:47:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223807993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194964\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221592920613\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n49 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy are you guys dropping kerbals on their heads?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey always drop on their head. Kinda like the sandwich on the spread side. And cats on their feet. There\u0027s gotta be some correlation I\u0027m missing...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-24T12:30:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf throw a Kerbal against a wall, he should crash the wall like a stone from catapult.\u003Cbr\u003E\nHe may lose the helmet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n***\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas there an achievement/competition?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ELate Kerbal Bombardment.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nDestroy \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E with the lowest number of hypersonic Kerbals from space\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}